Package: PMCfetchR
Title: Extract Full-Text Articles from NIH NCBI's PMC Articles Dataset in AWS Cloud
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Layla", "Bouzoubaa", , "lb3338@drexel.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6616-0950"))
Description: This package contains functions to make retrieving full-text biomedical 
  and life sciences articles from PMC's Articles Dataset easier by providing a way to convert PMIDs to PMCIDs
  and using those PMCIDs to fetch articles from an AWS S3 bucket. Fetched articles are returned tidied and tokenized by default.
